{"word":"G888 - ἀχρεῖος - achreîos - akh-ri'-os - Unprofitable","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀχρεῖος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">achreîos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">akh-ri'-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Unprofitable</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"பிரயோஜனமற்ற, அப்பிரயோஜனமான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"useless, good for nothing"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G5534 - χρή - chrḗ - khray/5534\">G5534</a> (compare <a href=\"#/G5532 - χρεία - chreía - khri'-ah/5532\">G5532</a>); <i>useless</i>, that is, (euphemistically) <i>unmeritorious:</i> - unprofitable.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}